Our next Special Guest for Cosplay World Richmond is none other than the incredible LISA MANCINI! 💫 She will be joining us at Cosplay World Richmond this June 15-16, 2024! ✨🚀 At the Greater Richmond Convention Center.

💥 @thereellisamancinerh 

Lisa Mancini is a full time cosplayer, illustrator and content creator from Ontario Canada. She is also known as a contestant from The Bachelor Canada and Bachelor in Paradise Canada. 

Lisa fell in love with the art of cosplay in 2018 when she attended her first Fan Expo Toronto. For the last 6 years, she has devoted her time to learning all areas of cosplay crafting such as 3D printing, sewing and foam work. Lisa prefers to create her own designs based on existing characters from comics, anime and video games. She is especially known for many mash-up creations such as Sub-Zero Elsa or Sailor Moon Knight.
